{
  "text": "Tobacco (Nitcotiana tabacum) BY-2 cells [CITATION_1] were transformed with A. tumefaciens stain LBA4404 containing the recombinant plasmid, V7-Gs5PTase8 by a co-cultivation method [CITATION_2] . The positive transformants were selected on the MS medium containing 50 mg/L kanamycin and the expression of the transgene was confirmed by qRT-PCR.",
